abstract: UnitedHealth Group reports second-quarter profit that beats expectations; analysts are disappointed by ratio of medical costs to premiums, which is higher than was expected.
lead_paragraph: UnitedHealth Group said on Thursday that its medical costs were about as expected during the second quarter, but analysts were disappointed.

headline.main: Largest U.S. Health Insurer Raises Profit Outlook for Year
